  <p>Open the Settings menu by tapping the Q-Tune logo or long pressing the footswitch while in Tuning mode. Settings are organized into multiple pages. Tap buttons to navigate and cycle through options. See <a href="#controls">Controls</a> for footswitch navigation shortcuts.</p>

